cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with the problem of assessing the adversarial robustness of deep neural network models, which is a common topic in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and cryptography (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of Monte Carlo methods, which are commonly used in the sub-field of neural networks (cs.NE).
